Figure S3A

suppressMessages(library(Seurat))
suppressMessages(library(ggplot2))
srt <- readRDS("/mnt/nmorais-nfs/marta/pA_karine/r_session/integrated_analysis_revised/integration/data/srt-total-dataset.rds")
Idents(srt) <- srt$RNA_snn_res.0.1
colors <- c("#F3C243",
            "#3FA8DF",
            "#095AB7",
            "#D60000",
            "#F78092",
            "#40A311",
            "#9DE75B",
            "#E05C00",
            "#00E08C",
            "#919392")
DimPlot(srt, reduction = "tsne", pt.size = 0.2, cols = colors, order = TRUE)

new_group <- srt$RNA_snn_res.0.1
new_group <- gsub(2,"2: T cells",new_group)
new_group <- gsub(9,"9: Fibroblasts",new_group)
new_group <- gsub(0,"0: Macrophages",new_group)
new_group <- gsub(1,"1: cDC2-Cd209a",new_group)
new_group <- gsub(3,"3: Macrophages (MCT-12h)",new_group)
new_group <- gsub(4,"4: cDC1-Ccl22",new_group)
new_group <- gsub(5,"5: NK cells",new_group)
new_group <- gsub(6,"6: cDC1-Clec9a",new_group)
new_group <- gsub(7,"7: Plasmacytoid DC",new_group)
new_group <- gsub(8,"8: Mast cells ",new_group)

srt$new_group <- new_group
DimPlot(srt, reduction = "tsne", pt.size = 0.2, cols = colors, group.by = "new_group") +
  theme(text = element_text(size = 25))
